high_descs: Go to the sink in the left corner of the room.
Pick up the potato that is next to the egg.
Go to the microwave to your left.
Cook the potato in the microwave.
Place the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato in the sink.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen sink to the far left of you
Pick up the potato in front of you
Turn around and go to the microwave that's should now be on your right
Put the potato in the microwave and heat it up
Take out the potato, then turn back around and go to the sink
Put the potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Heat up a potato, place the heated potato in the sink

high_descs: Turn 90 degrees to your right, walk to the fridge, turn 90 degrees to your right, and walk to the counter.
Pick up the potato next to the sink.
Turn 180 degrees, then turn another 90 degrees to the right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the potato inside, close the door, set the time, and when it's done cooking, take the potato out of the microwave and close it.
Turn around 180 degrees, then turn 90 degrees to the left and walk to the sink.
Place the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato found next to the sink in the microwave.
